
# Infrastructure

This directory contains Azure infrastructure definitions for **{{ project_name }}**
using [Bicep](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/azure-resource-manager/bicep/).

## Directory structure

```text
infra/
├── deploy.bicep                  # Subscription-scoped entry point (creates RG)
├── main.bicep                    # Resource-group-scoped orchestrator
├── modules/
│   ├── appInsights.bicep         # Application Insights
│   ├── keyVault.bicep            # Key Vault with RBAC
│   ├── logAnalytics.bicep        # Log Analytics workspace
{%- if use_redis %}
│   ├── redis.bicep               # Azure Cache for Redis (TLS, Entra auth, diagnostics, patching, firewall, persistence)
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_azure_openai %}
│   ├── openai.bicep              # Azure OpenAI Service (GPT + embeddings)
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_ai_search %}
│   ├── aiSearch.bicep            # Azure AI Search (vector/hybrid/semantic)
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_document_intelligence %}
│   ├── documentIntelligence.bicep # Azure Document Intelligence
{%- endif %}
{%- if database_backend == "azure_postgresql" %}
│   └── postgresFlexible.bicep    # Azure Database for PostgreSQL Flexible Server
{%- endif %}
├── parameters/
│   ├── dev/deploy.dev.bicepparam
│   ├── test/deploy.test.bicepparam
│   ├── staging/deploy.staging.bicepparam
│   └── prod/deploy.prod.bicepparam
└── scripts/
    ├── deploy.azcli              # Full subscription-scoped deployment
    ├── main.azcli                # Resource-group-scoped deployment
{%- if database_backend in ("postgresql", "azure_postgresql") %}
    ├── backup-db.zsh             # PostgreSQL backup utility
{%- endif %}
{%- if secret_backend == "azure_kv" %}
